{
  "lines": [
    {
      "key": "16.0",
      "line_index": 16,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "50739aed",
      "speaker": "フォニー",
      "ja": "部屋にいてくれたのね、それならちょうどいいわ",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "19.0",
      "line_index": 19,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "daa54b9c",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "何か用事？　今時間あるし、何でも言ってよ",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "24.0",
      "line_index": 24,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "e89a09e2",
      "speaker": "フォニー",
      "ja": "……まぁあなたがヒマかどうかはどうでもいいんだけど……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "26.0",
      "line_index": 26,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "1cdf23e5",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "珍しく歯切れの悪いフォニー。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "26.2",
      "line_index": 26,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "1cdf23e5",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "視線を少し落とし、言いにくそうにモジモジとしていた。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "30.0",
      "line_index": 30,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "78e102be",
      "speaker": "フォニー",
      "ja": "その、さ……この前のお礼……まだしていないって思って……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "33.0",
      "line_index": 33,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "7c84be8a",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "お礼……？　あれ？　俺何かしたっけ？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "38.0",
      "line_index": 38,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "eb5dfb96",
      "speaker": "フォニー",
      "ja": "ほら、精液のお礼……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "41.0",
      "line_index": 41,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "118f9ef",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "あ、ああ……それか……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "45.0",
      "line_index": 45,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "6b1bd4d3",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "（気持ち良かったし、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "45.2",
      "line_index": 45,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "6b1bd4d3",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "お礼とかそういうの全然考えていなかったな……）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "49.0",
      "line_index": 49,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "26a61fda",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "（してもらった立場だし、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "49.2",
      "line_index": 49,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "26a61fda",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "こっちがお礼しないとって思うくらいだし）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "54.0",
      "line_index": 54,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "de79f595",
      "speaker": "フォニー",
      "ja": "で、最近あんたちょっと疲れ気味だったでしょ？　だからコレ……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "56.0",
      "line_index": 56,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "91e443ca",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "フォニーはそういうと、ズボンの中から小瓶を一つ取り出す。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "60.0",
      "line_index": 60,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "afe5fb74",
      "speaker": "フォニー",
      "ja": "べ、別にヘンな物じゃないから……ただの栄養ドリンクよ",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "63.0",
      "line_index": 63,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "86770d26",
      "speaker": "フォニー",
      "ja": "い、言っとくけど！　お礼以上の意味はないから！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "63.4",
      "line_index": 63,
      "inline_index": 4,
      "line_hash": "86770d26",
      "speaker": "フォニー",
      "ja": "気まぐれで作っただけだし！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "67.0",
      "line_index": 67,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "7d5a04a4",
      "speaker": "フォニー",
      "ja": "そこのとこ勘違いしないでよね！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "70.0",
      "line_index": 70,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "744736f",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "（やれやれ……普通に手渡してくれたらいいのに。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "70.2",
      "line_index": 70,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "744736f",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "素直じゃないなフォニーは……）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "74.0",
      "line_index": 74,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "75fc3c50",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "（でもフォニーの心遣いには感謝しないとな）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "78.0",
      "line_index": 78,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "a1f8e63c",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "ありがとう、フォニー。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "78.2",
      "line_index": 78,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "a1f8e63c",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "確かに最近疲れ気味だったから嬉しいよ",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "82.0",
      "line_index": 82,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "56a8c1e8",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "さっそく飲ませてもらうよ",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "85.0",
      "line_index": 85,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "74d1f375",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "フォニーから小瓶を受け取ると、蓋を開ける。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "86.0",
      "line_index": 86,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "26e8dfa",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "若干不安にも思えたが匂いとかは特にせず、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "86.2",
      "line_index": 86,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "26e8dfa",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "問題もなさそうに思えた。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "89.0",
      "line_index": 89,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "58e5bad0",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "それじゃいただきます……んぐ……ん……？　う……うう……！？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "93.0",
      "line_index": 93,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "38e85977",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "（なに、これ……なんかヤバイ、やつかも……）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "96.0",
      "line_index": 96,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "7d346aae",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "急に身体が熱くなり、心音が跳ねるように鳴り響く。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "96.2",
      "line_index": 96,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "7d346aae",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "意識が朦朧としはじめ、景色がぐにゃぐにゃと歪む。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "102.0",
      "line_index": 102,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "ff9e7a07",
      "speaker": "フォニー",
      "ja": "えっ！？　ちょ、ちょっと？　フラフラして大丈夫！？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "107.0",
      "line_index": 107,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "81d2e1d9",
      "speaker": "フォニー",
      "ja": "べ、別にヘンな物入れてないんだけど！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "107.2",
      "line_index": 107,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "81d2e1d9",
      "speaker": "フォニー",
      "ja": "ちょっと待ってて！　今解毒剤を……！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "110.0",
      "line_index": 110,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "a198a9b3",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "う、あ……フォ……ニー……！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "117.0",
      "line_index": 117,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "742998",
      "speaker": "フォニー",
      "ja": "きゃぁぁっ！？　ちょ！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "117.2",
      "line_index": 117,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "742998",
      "speaker": "フォニー",
      "ja": "いきなり抱きかかえて何するつもりなのっ！？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "120.0",
      "line_index": 120,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "c77b920c",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "う、う、うう……！　欲しい……欲しい……！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "123.0",
      "line_index": 123,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "9898103f",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "フォニーの露になっていたパンツに手を掛けると、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "123.2",
      "line_index": 123,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "9898103f",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "破り捨てるように力任せにそれを強引に脱がす。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "128.0",
      "line_index": 128,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "618253c5",
      "speaker": "フォニー",
      "ja": "いやぁぁぁぁ！　やめてぇっ！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "130.0",
      "line_index": 130,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "69930d80",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "背後から抱きかかえられ、逃げ場のないフォニー。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "131.0",
      "line_index": 131,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "9cf8cab1",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "それでもこの場から逃れようと、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "131.2",
      "line_index": 131,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "9cf8cab1",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "懸命に身体を捩って抵抗する。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "133.0",
      "line_index": 133,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "2475a5a1",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "それでも男の力には敵わず、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "133.2",
      "line_index": 133,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "2475a5a1",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "されるがままになってしまっていた。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "136.0",
      "line_index": 136,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "160e8dd4",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "はぁ……！　はぁ！　お前が……お前が……欲しいぃぃぃぃ！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "139.0",
      "line_index": 139,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "6e9df4f4",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "限界まで勃起した肉棒を、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "139.2",
      "line_index": 139,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "6e9df4f4",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ぴったりと閉じたフォニーの割れ目に宛がう。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "140.0",
      "line_index": 140,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "29792afa",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "それで何をされるのか察したフォニーは必死に叫び抵抗を続ける。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "145.0",
      "line_index": 145,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "73c48264",
      "speaker": "フォニー",
      "ja": "ひっ！？　や、や……おちんちん……！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "145.2",
      "line_index": 145,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "73c48264",
      "speaker": "フォニー",
      "ja": "やめ……いやぁぁぁっ！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "150.0",
      "line_index": 150,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "534fa79f",
      "speaker": "フォニー",
      "ja": "や、やめ……わ、私初めてなのよっ！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "150.2",
      "line_index": 150,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "534fa79f",
      "speaker": "フォニー",
      "ja": "こ、こんな形で初めてを失うなんていやぁぁ……！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "152.0",
      "line_index": 152,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "9fcf9b90",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "豹変した{G_PlayerName}に恐怖し、瞳からは涙があふれる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "154.0",
      "line_index": 154,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "a32a5f30",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "どうにか{G_PlayerName}をやめさせようと、懸命にフォニーは訴え続けた。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "158.0",
      "line_index": 158,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "8430774d",
      "speaker": "フォニー",
      "ja": "あ……やめ、て……くれるの……？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "160.0",
      "line_index": 160,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "11d9557",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "フォニーの声が届いたのか、肉棒が割れ目から離れ安心するフォニー。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "161.0",
      "line_index": 161,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "67e793ba",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "しかしそれもつかの間、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "161.2",
      "line_index": 161,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "67e793ba",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "今度はフォニーのお尻の小さな蕾に肉棒の先端が当たる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "165.0",
      "line_index": 165,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "63096b92",
      "speaker": "フォニー",
      "ja": "ひっ！？　ま、待ちなさいっ！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "165.2",
      "line_index": 165,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "63096b92",
      "speaker": "フォニー",
      "ja": "そこお尻！　いや、やめ……あ、ああああ！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "179.0",
      "line_index": 179,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "c443fe54",
      "speaker": "フォニー",
      "ja": "んぅぅぅ！　ど、どこに入れてるのよぉっ！　早く抜きなさいっ！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "182.0",
      "line_index": 182,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "2004721a",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "──フンッ！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "186.0",
      "line_index": 186,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "100fdfbe",
      "speaker": "フォニー",
      "ja": "んほぉぉっ！♥　いや、いやぁぁぁ！！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "188.0",
      "line_index": 188,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "5e048faa",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "フォニーの言葉を遮るように、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "188.2",
      "line_index": 188,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "5e048faa",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "肉棒をミチミチと小さな蕾に捻じ込んでいく。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "191.0",
      "line_index": 191,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "5d5be66e",
      "speaker": "フォニー",
      "ja": "や、やめ……本当にダメぇっ！♥　これ以上入らないからぁっ！！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "194.0",
      "line_index": 194,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "ec809361",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "う、お……お、おおおっ！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "198.0",
      "line_index": 198,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "75f26069",
      "speaker": "フォニー",
      "ja": "んひぃぃぃっ！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "198.2",
      "line_index": 198,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "75f26069",
      "speaker": "フォニー",
      "ja": "お尻裂けちゃうぅ！♥　やめてよぉ……んんんっ！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "201.0",
      "line_index": 201,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "ae5d33ed",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "メス……メス……メスぅぅぅぅっ！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "210.0",
      "line_index": 210,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "a55cace9",
      "speaker": "フォニー",
      "ja": "はぎゅっ！♥　んおっ！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "210.2",
      "line_index": 210,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "a55cace9",
      "speaker": "フォニー",
      "ja": "待ってぇ♥　んぅ！♥　動かないでぇ！！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "213.0",
      "line_index": 213,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "5cae8378",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "フーッ！　フーッ！　ケツマンコイイ……！！　フーッ！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "216.0",
      "line_index": 216,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "e124bdf1",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "湧き上がる欲望の衝動に任せ、腰を突き上げる{G_PlayerName}。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "218.0",
      "line_index": 218,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "9cb4807c",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "小さなアナルをこじ開けるように押し広げられ、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "218.2",
      "line_index": 218,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "9cb4807c",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "奥に奥に深々と貫いていく。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "221.0",
      "line_index": 221,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "3a4ae670",
      "speaker": "フォニー",
      "ja": "あぎゅぅ♥　なんでこいつ……いきなり豹変して……んぐっ！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "224.0",
      "line_index": 224,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "d82ce10c",
      "speaker": "フォニー",
      "ja": "どうなっているのよぉ……ああぁっ♥",
      "zh": ""
